text: Georg Johansen (3 May 1924 - 4 July 1999) was a Norwegian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:1999 deaths Category:Norwegian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sarpsborg
